@node features "Features"

                               Features

-There's no complex installation: just run the game and play!

-Chain_Gang is a "Workbench" game, so it is meant to be played on the
 Workbench screen. The game window can be resized up to a maximum of
 640 x 400 pixels, and the game is redisplayed according to the new
 window size. If the window is too small, it will automatically be
 resized to an adequate displayable size.

-A 'minimize window' gadget which, when clicked on, will resize the
 game window to the minimum size possible but with the same tile size.

-A Top-10 records the best scores and saves them on disk.

-As the game uses as little of the computer's ressources as possible,
 you can run other applications, games, etc. at the same time.

-Chain_Gang works on all Amigas with Workbench 1.3 or higher.

@endnode

